headline: Wall Street Brunch: All Aboard The Earnings Train
summary: JPMorgan, Citi, BofA, Wells Fargo, Goldman and more on the calendar. Hot CPI could slash odds of rate cuts further. L.A. wildfires could be most costly ever.
